分析¶

DSSD$A_i$$E_i =kA_i+b $$(k,b)$$x_{im}$ $k_{x_{im}},b_{x_{im}}$x$m_x$, y$m_y$, xy $$ \begin{align} E_x=k\sum_\limits {i}A_{xi}+m_xb \\ E_y=k\sum_\limits {j}A_{yj}+m_yb \end{align} $$ $E_x=E_y$, $$ \text{x1es-y1es} = \sum_\limits {i}A_{xi}-\sum_\limits {j}A_{yj}=(m_y-m_x)\frac{b}{k} $$

  • $m_x=m_y$0

  • b

    • $\frac{b}{k}$-20.

,

(a) DSSD 15 16 :AB C D (Pedestal) (b) (a) 16 15 ( 100 ch) 16 15,

5. 利用拟合函数进行能量修正¶

Example1¶

In [14]:
c1->Clear();
c1->SetWindowSize(1200,400);
gStyle->SetOptStat(0);
c1->Divide(3,1);
c1->cd(1);
tree->Draw("x1es-y1es:x1es>>h1(200,0,8000,200,-100,100)",cdet1 && "x1hit==2 && y1hit==1","colz");
f1a = new TF1("f1a","+25+0.003*x",0,8000);
f1a->Draw("same");
gPad->SetLogz();
c1->cd(2);
tree->Draw("x1es-y1es-(25+0.003*x1es):x1es>>h2(200,0,8000,200,-100,100)",cdet1 && "x1hit==2 && y1hit==1","colz");
f1a = new TF1("f1a","0",0,8000);
f1a->Draw("same");
gPad->SetLogz();
c1->cd(3);
TCut cdxye1 = "abs(x1es-y1es-(25+0.003*x1es))<20";//
tree->Draw("x1es-y1es-(25+0.003*x1es):x1es>>h3(200,0,8000,200,-100,100)",cdxye1 && cdet1 && "x1hit==2 && y1hit==1","colz");
f1a = new TF1("f1a","0",0,8000);
f1a->Draw("same");
gPad->SetLogz();
c1->Draw();

每种情况可以用特定条件选择关联区域。或用函数关系进行修正后统一用两侧能量差选择关联条件。¶
